/ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1522219952880&subcate=latest&issue=20180328 |access-date=2018-03-28 |newspaper=[[明報|明報]]  |date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328164926/https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1522219952880&subcate=latest&issue=20180328 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180416-110156 |title=【字字珠璣】84歲楚原獲頒終身成就獎：明天總比昨天好！ |access-date=2018-04-19 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619142000/https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180416-110156 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他發表獲獎演說時透露，執導多部票房不濟的電影後計劃開拍《[[天龍八部|天龍八部]]》，但被[[方逸華|方逸華]]以可能虧蝕為由，在開鏡前一天撕走通告不讓開拍，並在辦公室教訓楚原「根本」不懂拍電影。<ref name="mingpao2">{{cite news |url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180416/s00016/1523815526331 |title=楚原擬拍《天龍八部》 方逸華：蝕本你有得賠？ |date=2018-04-16 |access-date=2018-04-16 |newspaper=明報 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618052354/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180416/s00016/1523815526331 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="appledaily">{{cite news |url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180415/58078099 |title=【金像獎】楚原自爆曾被六嬸嫌棄 終身成就獎得獎致辭值千金 |newspaper=香港蘋果日報 |date=2018-04-15 |access-date=2018-04-16 |language=zh-yue |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804142037/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180415/58078099 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2022年2月21日上午，楚原感到不適<ref name="楚原走了 無負此生">{{cite news |title=楚原走了 無負此生 |url=https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2443712/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%A5%9A%E5%8E%9F%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86-%E7%84%A1%E8%B2%A0%E6%AD%A4%E7%94%9F |page= |language= |publisher=星島日報 | date=2022-02-22 |accessdate=2022-02-22 |quote= |archive-date=2022-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222145033/https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2443712/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%A5%9A%E5%8E%9F%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86-%E7%84%A1%E8%B2%A0%E6%AD%A4%E7%94%9F |dead-url=no }}</ref>，送院留醫2小時後在中午病逝<ref name="楚原走了 無負此生" />，[[訃告|享壽]]87歲<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20220221/bkn-20220221211549773-0221_00862_001.html|title=名導演楚原離世 享年87歲|publisher=東網|date=2022-02-21|accessdate=2022-02-22|archive-date=2022-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220221151254/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20220221/bkn-20220221211549773-0221_00862_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。翌日，楚原兒子張詩樂發悼文，表示楚原遺願一切從簡，喪禮乃採私人形式，由家人閉門憑弔。<ref>{{cite news |title=楚原喪禮閉門舉行 兒子張詩樂悼念父親 「先父不負此生」 |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/local/20220222-314839 |accessdate=2022-04-29 |work=[[明報周刊|明報周刊]] |date=2022-02-22}}</ref>

